âœ… Troubleshooting Steps:
Check CPU, memory, disk â†’ top, free -m, df -h

Check application logs â†’ for errors or delays

Check web server â†’ Apache/Nginx status and logs

Check network â†’ ping, security groups, route tables

Check CloudWatch â†’ CPU, disk I/O, network metrics

Fix based on issue â†’ Restart app, resize EC2, optimize code

